N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4812.11 - Hours; occasions

State Regulations

All occasions of regular bingo shall be conducted between
the hours of 9 a.m. and 12 midnight and no more than three occasions of bingo
shall be conducted in the same premises during said hours. Notes
